cff-version: 1.2.0
title: articLLMate
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Monaghan
    given-names: Conal
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2949-5038"
repository-code: "https://github.com/ConalMonaghan/articLLMate"
license: MIT
date-released: "2026-06-29"
abstract: >-
  An R pipeline for LLM-assisted systematic review of methodological
  practices in published research. Supports multiple LLM providers
  (OpenAI, Gemini, Ollama), batch processing, and structured output
  mapping via configurable YAML schemas.
keywords:
  - systematic-review
  - large-language-models
  - psychometrics
  - response-validity
  - R
